{{Infobox comic strip
|title= Calvin and Hobbes
|image= [[File:Calvin and Hobbes Original.png|250px]]
|caption= Calvin and Hobbes take many wagon rides over the years. This one appears on the cover of the first collection of comic strips.
|author= [[Bill Watterson]]
|url= [http://www.calvinandhobbes.com/ Calvin and Hobbes]
|rss=
|atom=
|status= Concluded
|syndicate= [[Universal Press Syndicate]]
|publisher= [[Andrews McMeel Publishing, LLC|Andrews McMeel Publishing]]
