| implementations        = [[Allegro Common Lisp|Allegro CL]], [[Armed Bear Common Lisp|ABCL]], [[CLISP]], [[Clozure CL]], [[CMUCL]], [[Corman Common Lisp]], [[Embeddable Common Lisp|ECL]], [[GNU Common Lisp|GCL]], [[LispWorks]], [[Movitz]], [[Scieneer Common Lisp|Scieneer CL]], [[SBCL]], [[Genera (operating system)|Symbolics Common Lisp]]
