''Before Christ'' and ''Christian Era'' appear on the same page 252, while ''Vulgar Era'' appears on [http://books.google.com/books?id=ze8ehe65hwcC&amp;pg=RA2-PA250&amp;dq=%22Vulgar%22 page 250]
